cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ai-fdl-kit in your research or project, please cite it as below."
title: "ai-fdl-kit: Feature Definition Language for AI Code Generation"
abstract: >-
  A framework-agnostic specification language for defining software features
  as portable YAML blueprints. AI coding tools (Claude, Copilot, Cursor,
  ChatGPT, Gemini) consume blueprints to generate correct, complete
  implementations in any language or framework.
type: software
authors:
